{"article_id":"eZPlCuoJQK8fXz0U","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"This week in the Russia investigations :","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Rosenstein 's reprieve ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Rob Goldstone has a few more things to add","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and another paper avalanche on the way from the House intelligence committee .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein kept his job this week ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"which was a better outcome for him","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"than he thought .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"The embattled second in command at the Justice Department","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"- who is in primary command of the Russia investigation -","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"went to the White House on Monday","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"expecting to be terminated ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"as NPR 's Carrie Johnson reported .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"But that did n't happen .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"The account in The New York Times from the previous Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"as discussed last week ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"ultimately was not a sufficient tripwire for a president","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"who made his national brand in the firing business .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"Explanation , Vol . 1 :","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"Some reports suggested","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Rosenstein might simply have misjudged the seriousness","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"with which President Trump viewed the Times report , especially in a week","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"in which the president 's attention was in such heavy demand elsewhere","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"- first at the United Nations and then in the Senate Judiciary Committee .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"Explanation , Vol . 2 :","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump also explained his outlook in a news conference on Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"NPR 's Ayesha Rascoe asked him","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"whether he would fire Rosenstein .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Trump said this :","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"`` I would certainly prefer not doing that .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"There was no collusion .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"There was no obstruction .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"I mean ,","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"unless you call obstruction the fact","depth":14},{"id":33,"text":"that I fight back -","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"I do fight back ,","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"I really fight back .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"I mean ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"if you call that obstruction","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"that 's fine .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"But there 's no obstruction .","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"There 's no collusion -","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"I 'm going to meet with him tomorrow .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"I may call Rod tonight or tomorrow","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"and ask for a little bit of a delay to the meeting ,","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"because I do n't want to do anything","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"that gets in the way of this very important Supreme Court pick .","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"So I do n't want it competing and hurting the decision , one way or the other , decision . `` Again , I want to hear what she has to say ,","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"but I do n't want to do so -","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"I may delay that .","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"I 'm going to see .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"I do n't want to do anything","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that 's going to conflict with that .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"But my preference would be to keep them","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"and to let him finish up . ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"There were two points of interest in Trump 's answer .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"The first was that he connected Rosenstein","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"- and his fate -","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"directly to the Russia investigation and what Trump calls its lack of merit .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"But the second was that","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"the president said","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"he wanted to `` let him finish up , ''","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"suggesting","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"that Rosenstein is safe","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"until he and special counsel Robert Mueller finish their work .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Rob Goldstone was the last link in the chain of communication","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that started with the Russian government","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and ended with Donald Trump Jr.","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"As every pupil knows ,","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"a Russian attorney talked with billionaire Aras Agalarov ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"who talked with his son , singer Emin ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"who talked with Goldstone ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"who pinged Trump Jr. in a now-famous email .","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"Goldstone now says","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"a key detail in that much read , much dissected email was something","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"that he made up :","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"the detail about the `` crown prosecutor of Russia '' having been the one","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"who talked with Aras Agalarov .","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"Goldstone told NPR 's Miles Parks","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"he was just trying to inflate the importance of the person","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"who had set the chain of events in motion","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"that led to the subsequent meeting","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"in which Trump Jr. and other Trump campaign leaders hosted a delegation of Russians at Trump Tower .","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"Meaning what ?","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"If what Goldstone is saying now is accurate","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"- as opposed to what he said at the time in his message -","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"how much does it change the story of the Russia imbroglio ?","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"In terms of the substance and the potential political consequences , not much .","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"But it may say something about the tradecraft involved .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"In reading Goldstone 's email at the time","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Trump Jr. released it ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"many news organizations and analysts","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"- including NPR -","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"concluded","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"that what Goldstone was describing , in his own way , was a meeting between the elder Agalarov and Russia 's federal prosecutor , Yuri Chaika .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"That put the genesis for the outreach from the Russian government to the Trump campaign at the highest levels of the Russian government , and within a box within the organizational chart","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"connected to Russian President Vladimir Putin .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"That another lawyer was involved ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"especially if it was Natalia Veselnitskaya","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"- the one","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"who wound up flying to New York City for the meeting -","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"pushes the involvement of the Russian leadership further away .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"But overall , Goldstone 's account in a new book does not ameliorate the political and potential legal danger for the family Trump .","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"How so ?","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"If the Russia imbroglio is nothing else ,","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"it 's a story about how Trump Jr. and his other top counterparts may have accepted political dirt from a foreign government .","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"Among the lingering questions is whether they knew , then or since ,","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"they were doing so amid the broader campaign of active measures","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"waged by the Russians against the United States .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Or whether anyone may have taken part .","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"( The president has repeatedly denied","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"that he or anyone","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"associated with his campaign had any involvement in the Russian effort","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"to interfere in the 2016 election . )","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"At the time , Veselnitskaya gave an account of what she called illicit money from Russia","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"she said","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"was working its way into the Democratic National Committee ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"according to what people have said since .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Trump Jr. says","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"he took no action with that information ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"having expected easier-to-exploit dirt about Hillary Clinton .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Nonetheless , he received it .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"President Trump has acknowledged","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"that the meeting was to get information on the campaign 's opponents","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"but has said","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"that was `` totally legal . ''","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"Goldstone , meanwhile , wants out of all this .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"He told NPR 's Parks","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"he did n't know","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"whether the Trump campaign conspired with the Russians","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"who attacked the election","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"but","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"if that happened ,","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"it took place between those two sides .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Trump Jr. 's phone calls with Emin Agalarov were what arranged things ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"as Goldstone pointed out .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"He was not a party to it ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"he says .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"So","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"no matter what else happens in this imbroglio ,","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"Goldstone says","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"his chapter now is closed .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"He wants to move on .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"What remains to be seen is whether Mueller will permit that .","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"2018 has been the year of the paper war","depth":4},{"id":145,"text":"and members of Congress are reloading their weapons for another salvo .","depth":4},{"id":146,"text":"On Thursday , the House Judiciary Committee announced","depth":5},{"id":147,"text":"that it has issued a subpoena","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"to compel the Justice Department to produce the memos","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"that former FBI Deputy Director Andrew McCabe kept about his dealings in the Trump era .","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"McCabe followed the lead of then-FBI Director James Comey ,","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"who began writing notes about every interaction","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"he had with Trump","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"after their first meeting in New York City .","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"McCabe 's notes reportedly included the reference to Rosenstein 's discussion","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"about secretly recording Trump and who knows what else .","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"So Judiciary Committee Chairman Bob Goodlatte , R-Va. , wants that material .","depth":4},{"id":157,"text":"The following day , his compatriots on the House intelligence committee voted to release a number of transcripts of interviews","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"the panel had conducted","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"before concluding its Russia investigation earlier this year with a finding of no wrongdoing .","depth":5},{"id":160,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"led by Chairman Devin Nunes , R-Calif. ,","depth":6},{"id":162,"text":"voted to ask the Office of the Director of National Intelligence to declassify 53 interviews , from Akhmetshin , Rinat","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"- the Russian-American lobbyist","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"who attended the Trump Tower meeting -","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"to Yates , Sally , the former acting attorney general","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"who warned the White House about former national security adviser Mike Flynn .","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"The material from the House Republicans may not appear for some time ,","depth":4},{"id":168,"text":"but","depth":5},{"id":169,"text":"once it goes through the executive branch screening ,","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"look for another blizzard of evidence in the Russia imbroglio .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":341,"left":314,"right":340,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":314,"left":234,"right":313,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":174,"right":233,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":0,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":1,"right":172,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":172,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":233,"left":192,"right":232,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":182,"right":191,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":176,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":4,"right":175,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":180,"right":12,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":180,"left":179,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":178,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":177,"right":9,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"